# Rayvan Harness

Before meaningful work:

1. Read `AGENTS.md`
2. Read `ai/BOOTSTRAP.md`
3. Load at most two additional topical documents from the bootstrap routing table
4. Read the nearest nested `AGENTS.md` when working in a subtree that defines one

Use project subagents from `.cursor/agents/` according to `ai/BOOTSTRAP.md` orchestration. Prefer the main agent for simple work. Delegate only when context isolation or independent review justifies the cost.

Harness validation: `pnpm check:harness`
